divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside of my garage and looked into the sky (had a feeling I might see a balloon) and sure enough I saw what I thought was a balloon (the aliens often appear to me as balloons or balls of light that resemble balloons)but when I put them on the computer and enlarged the photo's they looked more like a v, albeit a sideways one. So I decided to post 'em I don't bother to post my observations very often because they usually look like balloons, and if I tell people they talk to me in my mind ... well then i'm a schizophrenic. I always wanted to meet aliens and I got my wish. Unfortunately I don't think they like me.
